Day 85: Create Files on App Servers using Ansible

Date: December 16, 2025
Overview
Dynamically created files using Ansible modules.
Key Concepts Learned

File module
Content generation
Directory creation
State management

Playbook
yaml- name: Create configuration directory
  file:
    path: /etc/myapp
    state: directory
    mode: '0755'

- name: Create config file
  file:
    path: /etc/myapp/config.txt
    state: touch
    mode: '0644'

Challenges Faced
Managing file states and ensuring idempotency across multiple runs.
